name: "L'IMPERATORE"
description:
Four is my number, cubic is my throne.I am stability, the steady hand that holds and supports.I am the leader and point of reference of this world, patriarch and ruler.
.
.
.
This card is part of an original tarot deck made by Rahtattoo. 
The 22 works that compose it are the result of the study of the ancient symbolism that animates the tarot's major arcana.
